yo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mixed event\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the first ever mixed-gender swimming contest\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB won the gold inJapan, with USA claiming first prize in Paris, ahead ofChinain silver and the Aussies in bronze place.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999997683062, \"rank\": 2.2946022389101149e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999011157857831, \"rank\": 9.809009100211308e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.9932693316830208e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"inJapan\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"first prize\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"ahead ofChinain silver\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aussies\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze place\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, three-time Olympic medallist forAustraliaJames Magnussen is no fan of the event, questioning whether it should be in the Games at all.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three-time Olympic medallist forAustraliaJames Magnussen\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"no fan\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would call it the egg-and-spoon race of theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the egg-and-spoon race\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is farcical,' Magnussen said on the Matty and the Missile inParispodcast.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Magnussen\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"the Matty\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the Missile inParispodcast\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have got men swimming against women.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kaylee McKeown won the gold medal in the 100m backstroke, she goes up againstRyan Murphy, who got bronze in the men's 100m backstroke.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m backstroke\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"againstRyan Murphy\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is about a 15m difference.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 15m difference\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'On their own, they are both amazing products \\u2026 I do not know why we'd want to compare male athletes and female athletes.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing products\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"male athletes\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then the race itself just ends up this absolute jungle, where one person's ten metres ahead, then the other team switches.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"this absolute jungle\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the other team\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got male breaststrokers vs female breaststrokers.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"male breaststrokers\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"female breaststrokers\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's just a shambles of an event.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a shambles\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not understand why it's at the Olympic Games, and I can not understand giving out Olympic medals to that event.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"that event\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are telling me at the end of the day that that's worth the same as individual gold for Ariarne Titmus in the 400m freestyle?\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"individual gold\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m freestyle\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not comparable.'\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aussie legend Stephanie Rice won three golds in the pool at Beijing 2008 and she too has doubts about the mixed event.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1653, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Rice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephanie Rice\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Rice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Rice\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three golds\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"Beijing\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed event\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel very mixed about it.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like it's a token event.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a token event\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the sense that it feels more fun, than a purist race,' she said on Stan Sports' Olympic Daily.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1890, \"end\": 1901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_(service)\", \"score\": 0.9999999450328703, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stan Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_(service)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_(service)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sense\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"a purist race\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I like that swimming is looking at different ways of evolving.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"different ways\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the same as the men having an 800 metre freestyle and the women having a 1500 metre freestyle.'\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"an 800 metre freestyle\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngra